setInfo.name: EX Ruby & Sapphire
setInfo.description: The first set in the EX Series, introducing Generation III Pokémon from the Hoenn region. Features the debut of Pokémon-ex cards with high HP and powerful attacks, but giving up two Prize cards when knocked out. Includes popular Hoenn starters Treecko, Torchic, and Mudkip with their evolutions.
